text: Abdul Wahed is a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politician and the former Member of Parliament of Kushtia-2. ==Career== Wahed was elected to parliament from Kushtia-2 as a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Abdul Wahed (politician)
